<h2 id="medya-ve-iletisim-okuyanlar-ne-kadar-maas-alir" class="wp-block-heading">What are the salaries for media and communication graduates?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most frequently asked questions by those aspiring to a career in media and communication is about salaries in this field. In Turkey, the salaries of media and communication graduates vary depending on the sector they work in, their experience level, and the city they are in.</p>
