<div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]">
<div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling">
<p data-start="0" data-end="598" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Yes, studying architecture in Türkiye is not only possible but also highly advantageous. Well-established schools like Istanbul Technical University (İTÜ), Middle East Technical University (ODTÜ), Yıldız Technical University (YTÜ), and Mimar Sinan Fine Arts University (MSGSÜ) offer both theoretical and practical education. An architecture education in Türkiye provides students with the opportunity to <strong data-start="337" data-end="453">learn about historical and contemporary architecture simultaneously, develop projects, and participate in international competitions</strong>. Furthermore, due to the sector&#8217;s growth, urban renewal projects, and design-focused initiatives, there are ample career opportunities for graduates.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
