<h2 id="turkiyede-savunma-sanayii-ve-havacilik-sektorune-giris-ilk-adimlar" class="wp-block-heading">Entering the Defense and Aviation Sectors in Turkey: First Steps</h2>
<h4 data-start="243" data-end="276">Education and Academic Preparation</h4>
<ul data-start="277" data-end="668">
<li data-start="277" data-end="398">
