<h2 id="turkiyedeki-savunma-sanayii-sirketleri-kariyer-firsatlari-ve-staj-imkanlari" class="wp-block-heading">Defense Industry Companies in Turkey: Career and Internship Opportunities</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is home to many major defense industry companies. These companies offer various career opportunities for students and recent graduates. Prominent companies include:</p>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>ASELSAN:</strong> A leading company in electronics and defense systems. It offers internships and job opportunities.</li>
<li><strong>TUSAŞ (Turkish Aerospace Industries):</strong> A company working on aviation and space technologies. It provides internship opportunities for students.</li>
<li><strong>ROKETSAN:</strong> A company that develops rocket and missile systems. It offers career opportunities for interns and recent graduates.</li>
</ul>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Interning at these companies will help you increase your industry experience and shape your career.</p>
<h2 id="turkiyenin-en-buyuk-savunma-sanayi-sirketi-hangisi" class="wp-block-heading">Which is Turkey&#8217;s Largest Defense Industry Company?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey&#8217;s largest defense industry company is ASELSAN. Founded in 1975, ASELSAN undertakes major projects in the fields of electronic systems and defense technologies. The company is involved in numerous projects both domestically and internationally and is continuously growing. ASELSAN aims to attract young talent to the sector by offering career and internship opportunities.</p>
<h2 id="savunma-sanayiinde-calismak-icin-hangi-bolum-okunmali" class="wp-block-heading">What Major Should You Study to Work in the Defense Industry?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To work in the defense industry, engineering disciplines are the most suitable. The following majors are particularly recommended:</p>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Aerospace Engineering</strong></li>
<li><strong>Electrical-Electronics Engineering</strong></li>
<li><strong>Mechanical Engineering</strong></li>
<li><strong>Computer Engineering</strong></li>
<li><strong>Defense Technologies</strong></li>
</ul>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These majors offer students the opportunity to participate in innovative projects in the sector and develop their careers.</p>
<h2 class="JlqpRe"><span class="JCzEY tNxQIb"><span class="CSkcDe">Which is bigger, ASELSAN or TUSAŞ?</span></span></h2>
<p data-start="0" data-end="150">In Turkey, both <strong data-start="15" data-end="26">ASELSAN</strong> and <strong data-start="34" data-end="86">TUSAŞ (TAI – Turkish Aerospace Industries, Inc.)</strong> are very important in the sector, but they differ based on size criteria:</p>
<ul data-start="152" data-end="533">
<li data-start="152" data-end="332">
<p data-start="154" data-end="332"><strong data-start="154" data-end="165">ASELSAN</strong>: It is Turkey&#8217;s largest defense company in terms of revenue, number of employees, and R&#038;D investment. It is a leader in electronic systems, radar, communication, and defense solutions.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="333" data-end="533">
<p data-start="335" data-end="533"><strong data-start="335" data-end="350">TUSAŞ (TAI)</strong>: It is Turkey&#8217;s leading company in the aviation and space fields; it is a pioneer in aircraft, helicopter, UAV, and satellite projects. However, its <strong data-start="467" data-end="530">revenue and number of employees are generally lower than ASELSAN&#8217;s</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="535" data-end="661">In general, ASELSAN is Turkey&#8217;s largest defense industry company, while TUSAŞ is the leader in the aviation and space sector.</p>
