oftware-development-in-turkey/#webpage"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/advantages-of-studying-it-and-software-development-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="JlqpRe"><span class="JCzEY tNxQIb"><span class="CSkcDe">What is the Size of Turkey&#8217;s Software Sector?</span></span></h2>
<div class="p8Jhnd">
<div class="aj35ze">
<article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" tabindex="-1" data-turn-id="request-WEB:c9d72db5-aa10-4e0f-acf8-dc90470f8b75-21" data-testid="conversation-turn-44" data-scroll-anchor="true" data-turn="assistant">
<div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] thread-sm:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] thread-lg:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)">
<div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] thread-lg:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1">
<div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow">
<div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="53a98224-4665-4b3f-923c-e9879a8a233f" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-mini">
<div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]">
<div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling">
<p data-start="0" data-end="425">Turkey&#8217;s software sector has shown remarkable development in recent years, recording significant growth. As of 2023, Turkey&#8217;s information and communication technologies (ICT) sector reached a size of 784.6 billion TRY, an 83% increase in TRY terms compared to the previous year. A large portion of this growth has been driven by rapid development in the software and services categories.</p>
<h2 data-start="601" data-end="637">A Rich Education and Talent Pool</h2>
<p data-start="639" data-end="979">In Turkey, departments like computer engineering, software engineering, data science, and artificial intelligence offer both theoretical and practical education. International students can easily study through programs taught in English. Additionally, short-term bootcamps and online courses help students quickly adapt to the industry.</p>
<h2 data-start="986" data-end="1019">Excellent Job and Internship Opportunities</h2>
<p data-start="1021" data-end="1411">Turkey has a strong business ecosystem for software developers. Major tech companies like Trendyol, Peak Games, and Yemeksepeti offer internship and job opportunities for international students. The startup ecosystem also provides project experience and entrepreneurial opportunities for young software developers. Freelance work opportunities allow students to participate in global projects.</p>
<h2 data-start="1787" data-end="1832">Global Work and Freelance Opportunities</h2>
<p data-start="1834" data-end="2084">For software developers, geographical limitations have largely disappeared. It&#8217;s possible to work on projects worldwide by working <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-freelance-calisma/">freelance or remotely</a> from Turkey. This offers international students the chance to gain both experience and income.</p>
<h2 data-start="2091" data-end="2130">Networking and Professional Development</h2>
<p data-start="2132" data-end="2401">In Turkey, hackathons, tech fairs, and coding competitions help international students develop their skills and build connections in the industry. International job prospects can be enhanced with certifications from AWS, Google, and Microsoft.</p>
<h2 data-start="2408" data-end="2441">Cultural and Language Advantages</h2>
<p data-start="2443" data-end="2702">While studying in Turkey, international students have the opportunity to <strong data-start="2498" data-end="2538">experience both European and Asian cultures</strong> and can participate in job and internship projects in either English or Turkish. This helps them advance their careers on a global scale.</p>
<h2 data-start="2443" data-end="2702">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<div id="model-response-message-contentr_5530edfe3c2153c4" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" dir="ltr">
<h3>Does software development have a bright future?</h3>
<p>Yes, software development has a very bright future with the growth of fields like digital transformation, artificial intelligence, and automation. New technologies are constantly emerging.</p>
<h3>What is the importance of domestic software?</h3>
<p>Domestic software increases technological independence and cybersecurity. It contributes to the economy, prevents brain drain, and ensures that critical data remains within the country.</p>
<h3>Why is software development important?</h3>
<p>Software is a critical tool for creating solutions to problems, increasing efficiency, and encouraging innovation. It makes life easier for businesses and individuals.</p>
<h3>What is Turkey&#8217;s global ranking in software?</h3>
<p>Turkey ranks within the top 20 in international rankings and is a rapidly rising country in the software sector. The exact ranking can vary depending on different reports.</p>
<h3>What is the largest software company in Turkey?</h3>
<p>The largest software company in Turkey can vary depending on different criteria such as revenue, number of employees, and market value. Some of the most well-known companies in this field include firms like <b>Logo Yazılım</b> and <b>OBSS</b>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mt-3 w-full empty:hidden">
<div class="text-center"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
